  "title": "Source Document Node Access Methods",
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "Source document nodes can be accessed directly via `GET /workspaces/{ws_id}/nodes/{node_id}`, via the dedicated `GET /workspaces/{ws_id}/source-documents` endpoint, and via the \"View source paragraph\" link in the node editor sidebar."
